OL,3,CBeckham says football must 'come
OL,4,Ctogether' to help ex-players with
OL,5,Cdementia
OL,7,FDavid Beckham has backed a campaign to
OL,8,Fimprove care for former players
OL,9,Faffected by neurodegenerative diseases
OL,10,Fby demanding more from the football
OL,11,Fauthorities.
OL,13,FThe former Manchester United star has
OL,14,Fgiven his support to the Football
OL,15,FFamilies for Justice (FFJ) campaign,
OL,16,Fwhich is working on giving powers to
OL,17,Ffootball's independent regulator to
OL,18,Fforce the games authorities to take
OL,19,F"decisive action" on neurodegenerative
OL,20,Fdiseases among ex-players.
