OL,3,CBeckham says football must 'come
OL,4,Ctogether' to help ex-players with
OL,5,Cdementia
OL,7,FThe campaign is also working alongside
OL,8,Fthe Greater Manchester Mayor Andy
OL,9,FBurnham and the Mayor of the Liverpool
OL,10,FCity Region Steve Rotheram.
OL,12,FBeckham said in a video address played
OL,13,Fat the Dementia in Football event in
OL,14,FManchester: "We need the football
OL,15,Ffamily to come together and allocate
OL,16,Fresources to help address the tragedy
OL,17,Fof these devastating diseases.
OL,19,F"Let's ensure that victims and their
OL,20,Ffamilies are treated with kindness,
OL,21,Frespect and best in class support."
