OL,3,CBeckham says football must 'come
OL,4,Ctogether' to help ex-players with
OL,5,Cdementia
OL,7,FFFJ wants the football authorities to
OL,8,Fdevelop a care and support scheme for
OL,9,Fplayers who develop dementia or other
OL,10,Fneurodegenerative conditions linked to
OL,11,Ftheir careers, and a requirement that
OL,12,Fthe scheme must be agreed with past
OL,13,Fand present players and their families.
OL,15,FStiles said that the Professional
OL,16,FFootballers' Association (PFA) is
OL,17,F"morally bankrupt" and criticised
OL,18,Fefforts made so far to tackle this
OL,19,Fissue.
