OL,5,Cdementia
OL,7,FHe described the Football Brain Health
OL,8,FFund, set up with an initial #1million
OL,9,Fby the PFA and the Premier League in
OL,10,F2023, as a PR exercise.
OL,12,F"Football is so wealthy they could
OL,13,Fsort this out tomorrow, but we're
OL,14,Fnowhere near getting that.
OL,16,F"I am so glad these gentlemen (Burnham
OL,17,Fand Rotheram) are going to take it
OL,18,Fonto another level," Stiles said at a
OL,19,Fmeeting in central Manchester.
